# Diamond Dot for "i" in Pride

This file should be replaced with a small diamond image (about 8x8 pixels) that will be used as the dot above the "i" in "Pride".

Instructions:
1. Create or find a small diamond image (golden color preferred)
2. Save it as "diamond-dot.png" in this folder
3. Recommended size: 8x8 pixels to 12x12 pixels
4. Format: PNG with transparent background

The CSS will use this image to replace the dot on the "i" in "Pride".
